constructor.details: Constructor to initialize the contract with token addresses and admin.

params._rewardToken1: Address of the first reward token.
params._rewardToken2: Address of the second reward token.
params._stakeToken: Address of the token to be staked.

params.rate1: The new reward rate for the first reward token.
params.rate2: The new reward rate for the second reward token.

params.amount: The amount of tokens to stake.
The amount of tokens to withdraw.

params.token: The address of the token to withdraw.

admin.details: Admin role for managing the contract.

rewardRate1.details: Reward rate for the first reward token.

rewardRate2.details: Reward rate for the second reward token.

userStakes.details: Mapping of user addresses to their staked token amounts.
